description:
The Apostles' Creed | Full-Length Version | Episode 17 | The Great Retrieval

Session 17: The Great Retrieval compares the Creed to the redemption narrative revealed in Scriptures and explores the significance of promised resurrection for all believers. 

The Apostle's Creed is a Universal Creed for the Universal Church.  The amazing document is a vibrant, living expression of the heart of faith.  This 17-part series traces the origin of the Apostles Creed, placing it in its historical context. An international and interdenominational cast of notable theologians discuss each phrase of the Creed, emphasizing its relevance and application to our lives today.

Director: T.N. Mohan, Angela Burchett
Starring: Dr. Timothy George, Pastor Langdon Palmer
